<br>
I also have a 50+ druid and a twinked monk and I would suggest NOT going the normal route.  Try zones that you didn't do as a druid.  Try things you *couldn't* have done as a druid.  I've now spent some time in Kurn's (great xp bonus), UGuk which was a lot of fun, and once I get 250 tailoring out of the way on my druid I hope to spend time in places like SolA and B, CC (well, for ore mostly.  I spent lotsa druidy time there), Paludal (xp is awesome, and it's kind of a cool zone to boot), Kaesora, and just dungeons in general.  I figure it will be a great place to learn monkly skills, with the cushion of my equipment if I mess up too badly.<br>
<br>
I did a fair range of places leveling up my druid, including all the places you mentioned.  I, however, got tired of all of them in less than a level.  Probably 90% of my hunting time was on mobs that dropped tailoring ingredients <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .  I'm trying to use my monk not only to get more ingredients while I need them, but to see some places and do some things that I couldn't before.  <br>
<br>
YMMV,<br>
<br>
Littlun. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1832.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1832.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1832.topic&index=0><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1832.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.threadControl?topicID=1832.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1832.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1832.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="monklybusiness43508frm13">Board Rules<option value="monklybusiness43508frm1">General<option value="monklybusiness43508frm16">New Features<option value="monklybusiness43508frm2">Guides and Tactics<option value="monklybusiness43508frm3"